rComments: He's a nice guy and always smiles, but he's the most boring person I've ever met. On top of that, I don't like the way he explains topics nor do I like this seminar. The weekly writing assignments aren't too hard but they're really annoying, also you'll have a lot of readings to do for the midterm. Wouldn't highly recommend this course/seminar.
Very helpful and he's very enthusiastic about the material. Willing so spend time with students if they do not understand hard concepts.
Lovely man, so approachable, bright as hell.
